data.description:
Welcome to your country retreat in Edgewood! This mobile home sits on an acre and a half, perfect opportunity for horse loving people! Being sold as-is, cash purchase, needs some tlc and and elbow grease. A new septic system is needed and repairs are needed for the permanent foundation certification. Mobile home title has been deactivated and it's ready to be sold. Sellers will not make any repairs!

Conveniently located, this property offers easy access to both Albuquerque and Santa Fe. With Albuquerque just a short 20-minute drive away, and the cultural hub of Santa Fe within an hour's reach, you'll enjoy the best of both worlds — the tranquility of country living and the amenities of two vibrant cities.

Don't miss this opportunity to make this home your own.
